{"tid":2259974,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"付國豪庭上笑言以為郭家麒要拿刀殺他 認當日表現談笑風生 願向郭家麒道歉","createTime":"2020-10-27T08:26:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T09:07:16.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7b9da5ad42d6e91725ceba062d55ca0a0feac023","tid":2259974,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T08:26:00.000Z","msg":"自稱《環球網》記者的內地人付國豪去年8月在機場遭示威者圍堵及襲擊，案件今續審。付國豪接受辯方盤問，其中代表兼職侍應賴雲龍的大狀指，立法會議員郭家麒曾叫在場人士不要行私刑，並聲言「你叫佢跪低，你叫佢平反六四，但係唔可以咁樣」；付今一度答稱當時不知道郭是好是壞，更「開玩笑」稱以為郭要拿刀刺殺他，惟他隨即向不在庭上的郭致歉。<br />\n<br />\n辯方指，當時付的表情「好cool」、「神態輕鬆，談笑風生」，付表示表面上是如此，但他的實際心情不「酷」，而是「苦」，「具體來說是苦中作樂，在一種無奈的狀態中」。<br />\n<br />\n辯方亦指，郭家麒在有線片段中向在場人士謂：「你叫佢道歉，你叫佢跪低，你叫佢平反六四，但你唔可以咁樣。」付表示對郭上述的話沒印象，只記得郭當時站在他身邊。付又謂，雖然很感謝郭，但當時連他是好是壞也不知道。付隨即再謂：「開個玩笑，我當時甚至還以為他要拿刀刺殺我。對不起，郭議員。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201027/5EAJOFLLXFFUPEWVSMOMS7WRFY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201027%2F5EAJOFLLXFFUPEWVSMOMS7WRFY%2F&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETUzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=552372c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201027%2F5EAJOFLLXFFUPEWVSMOMS7WRFY%2F&h=631a3a3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201027/5EAJOFLLXFFUPEWVSMOMS7WRFY/</a>"},{"pid":"454d74eb4f57bcf126596d1593ce59700dbb6ebe","tid":2259974,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T08:27:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"697a0c56af8aa4c403591c29da5164c1c07c4394","tid":2259974,"uid":241804,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T08:27:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wb51iqz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWb51iqz.png&h=969e1232&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dfc757600f72e6d03a6ea3e10daf2be5d72ff38e","tid":2259974,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"697a0c56af8aa4c403591c29da5164c1c07c4394","tid":2259974,"uid":241804,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T08:27:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wb51iqz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWb51iqz.png&h=969e1232&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T08:28:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26ff7aef48f70eff73a4729843270126969ff89e","tid":2259974,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T08:29:29.000Z","msg":"佢知唔知咩係六四都成問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e5b95436f763309e7cb20e8e9da2d14c3dfc8d","tid":2259974,"uid":241804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfc757600f72e6d03a6ea3e10daf2be5d72ff38e","tid":2259974,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"697a0c56af8aa4c403591c29da5164c1c07c4394","tid":2259974,"uid":241804,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T08:27:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wb51iqz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWb51iqz.png&h=969e1232&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T08:28:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T08:29:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im